踢（腿）；踹；踢蹬；反抗；抗议；戒除（瘾）；踢进（球门）得分；射击时后坐
踢；极大的乐趣；（毒品或酒精的）效力；刺激性；极度兴奋；极度刺激

sogou-CET4.vphr: (kick around)非正式地讨论; 随便谈谈[出现1次)];(kick in the pants)鞭挞[出现1次)];(kick out)强使离开; 赶走[出现1次)]

0.cn: 踢了，孩子真的踢了一下。

2.en: But faster, OK? Now, claw, kick, claw, kick. I'm stalking the prey. Claw, kick.
2.cn: 但速度要快一点，像这样，划、踢，划、踢 匍匐前进，划、踢。

3.en: Even simpler this time, kick the ball with your foot.
3.cn: 这次更简单了，用你的脚踢球。

4.en: No, I don't want to hit you. Oh what then? Kick me? No. Bite me?
4.cn: 不，我不想打你。什么？你要踢我？不咬我？

5.en: No, it's a gentle kick; you're doing it wrong. Here. Give me those.
5.cn: 不，人家是轻踢，你没做到位。来，把东西都给我。

6.en: No, no. you're okay. If you run into crocodiles, just kick them with your boots.
6.cn: 不，不，没事，如果你碰到鳄鱼，就用靴子踢它。

7.en: Wait. If she only has one leg, shouldn't she be on can't-kick-starter?
7.cn: 慢着，如果她只有一条腿，她应该去"踢不了人"那种网站才对吧。

8.en: You don't need my help when you can open the trunk with a simple kick of the foot.
8.cn: 当轻轻一踢就可以打开后备箱时，你就根本不需要我帮忙了。

9.en: Julie, isn't that great? I mean, isn't that just kick-you-in-the-crotch, spit-on-your-neck fantastic?
9.cn: 真是太棒了！是不是像踢你的裤裆和朝你的脖子吐口水一样神奇？

10.en: What are you doing? I felt a kick. There's a baby in there. Oh, yeah, that's where I put it.
10.cn: 你在干嘛我感觉到踢了一下，里面有一个宝宝呢。对哦，原来我把宝宝放这里了。

11.en: All right, she's right. We gotta get serious. Let's put Styrofoam peanuts down his pants and kick him.
11.cn: 她说的对，我们得认真一点儿。让我们把这个塞到他的裤裆里，然后踢他！

12.en: Yeah, you missed, 'Takes money to make money,' and 'Don't make me come down there and kick your wall street butt.'
12.cn: 你错过了“用钱去赚钱”还有，“别逼我过去踢你的华尔街屁股”。

13.en: But he was faster than me, stronger than me and he would kick my butt, and we both knew that, so I just took it in.
13.cn: 但是他跑得比我快，长得比我壮，他会踢我的屁股，我们都知道，所以我只是默默承受。

14.en: I think what my colleague is saying is that you're not seeing the possibilities here. That is indeed one unbelievably kick ass computer.
14.cn: 我想我同事想说的是你没有看到这里面的潜力，这是一款另人难以置信的产品，可以把其它电脑一脚踢出门外。

15.en: He had worked tremendously hard pre-season, oh I was like, "man, this is a blow. I mean, this is a kick in the stomach right here."
15.cn: 他已经在赛季前付出了巨大的努力，所以我想，“天啊，这是一个大打击啊” 我的意思是，这就像一脚，刚好踢在你的肚子上

16.en: Can you hear a little heart beat? Yes, I can. It's going "Boom. Boom. Boom." Oh, it just moved. Yes, sometimes babies give a little kick.
16.cn: 你有没有听到小宝宝的心跳声？我听到了，就像这样，“砰！”“砰”！“砰！”哇，他刚才动了一下。是的，有时候小宝宝在里面会踢我肚子。

17.en: What a big house. Lots of room for a Queen to kick a ball about. Where is the Queen?
17.cn: 好大的房子！空间这么大，女王可以在这里踢球了。女王在哪里呢？

18.en: All right, so, shh! Tyra Banks is about to kick someone off America's Next Top Model.
18.cn: 好吧，大家安静！泰拉·班克斯(超模之母)马上要从全美超模大赛里踢人了。

19.en: What a big house. Lots of room for a Queen to kick a ball about. Where is the Queen? Queen? Queen? Where are you?
19.cn: 好大的房子！空间这么大，女王可以在这里踢球了。女王在哪里呢？女王，女王，你在哪里？
